verses.text:
Nothing for Jesus! O fearful thought it;
Grateful to you you never seem to be;
Nothing for Jesus, when he has given All;
Nothing for Jesus, when you are rich and free.

Nothing for Jesus! O you youth and maiden, Have you no music for the ear?
Nothing for Jesus, you who own his riches;
Nothing for Jesus in your youth so dear.

Nothing for Jesus! Let not standing, it would be
Something yet to repent, an aid to all; in vain;
Nothing for Jesus, when he gave all that he had;
Nothing for Jesus, when you know you're saved.

Something for Jesus, Something for Jesus;
Let not another day pass by;
Something for Jesus, Something for Jesus;
He gave his all for you and I.
